translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: After two weeks of silence, the terrorist group called "Zombie Exterminators", also know as "ZE" or "Exterminators", has been seen once again near Petr√≥polis and Alto da Serra.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: It was believed that the group was disbanded after the death of Silva, ex-leader of the group. The Brazillian Military Force Command hasn't pronounced about it yet.
